on 2: Our Physical Nature </div><div class="t mb34 x73 h27 y1c66 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READ FOR THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Ps. 8:1-9. </div><div class="t m312 x73 h27 y746 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: 1 Corinthians 6:19. </div><div class="t m1cc x73 h27 y13d9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHT: How is our physical well-being related to being </div><div class="t m1be8 x60 h27 y138d ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">created in God&apos;s image? </div><div class="t m774 x73 h27 y1c6b ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE: </div><div class="t m25a x60 h27 y1401 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Molded From Clay (Gen. 2:7; 3:17-19; Eccles. 3:19, 20). </div><div class="t m141a x60 h27 y12d7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Affected by Sin (Gen. 3:16-19). </div><div class="t mcf3 x60 h27 y1078 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">None of These Diseases (Exod. 15:26). </div><div class="t m634 x60 h27 y1112 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Health and Healing (Ps. 103:1-5). </div><div class="t m1952 x60 h27 y1ccb ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Body Temples (2 Cor. 6:16-18). </div><div class="t m165e x73 h27 y152e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible Study Guide in Braille </div><div class="t m3ba x60 h27 y11bc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The regular adult Sabbath School Bible Study Guides are available </div><div class="t mf0b x73 h27 yeea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">free each month in Braille and 16 2/3 rpm records to blind and physically </div><div class="t md7 x73 h27 ybbf ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">handicapped persons who cannot read normal ink print. This includes </div><div class="t mbe8 x73 h27 y1062 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individuals who, because of arthritis, multiple sclerosis, paralysis, acci-</div><div class="t m7f6 x73 h27 y14d0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dent, old age, and so forth cannot hold or focus on normal ink-print </div><div class="t m1572 x73 h27 y19dd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">publications. Contact the Christian Record Services, Box 6097, Lincoln, </div><div class="t m40d x48 h27 y1559 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">N